Customer

1. Should be able to select city
2. SHould be able to see all Movies in that city
3. Upon selection of Movie and particular date , should be able to see all shows of that movie
4. Upon selection of show , Should be able to select type of seat and seats
5. Make payment and book
6. Should be able to view his ticket details

BookMyShow system

1. Add/update city 
2. Add/update movie into city
3. Add/update theatre into city
4. Add/update show
5. Show vacant seats of a theatre , handle concurrency of seat booking
6. Generate ticket id 
7. Send notifications via mail , messages about ticket and show


